Maxima made her way to the conference room. 

Striding in, her crimson optics glanced about. She had become confortable 
with her form by now. Her old existance was now gone.. a new existance lay ahead 
of her. When she was out in the wilderness, it all seemed to guide her, click 
within her, hit her with the reality of it all. Now.. she knew that there was 
a path that Alpha Trion had forseen ... a path only she could take. No Autobot 
she fought could walk her path. It was a giant leap for a peaceful old bot 
like Alpha Trion to take. 

As she moved into the conference room. "What is it that you want?" Her voice 
was rather pleasant. 

--part1_15b.26464ec7.2cbf73a3_boundary
